This paper focuses on the use of explanations in automated platforms that support users in finding mutually beneficial matches, such as online dating and job recruitment sites. Therefore, the most likely category is Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC), which deals with the design, evaluation, and implementation of interactive computing systems for human use. Information Retrieval (cs.IR) is also a likely category, as the paper discusses the use of recommender systems to assist users in finding suitable matches. Cybersecurity and Privacy (cs.CY) is another possible category, as the paper may touch on issues related to privacy and security in online dating platforms. Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) is also a possible category, as the paper discusses the use of automated platforms to facilitate social connections. Finally, Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) is a possible category, as the paper may discuss the use of natural language processing techniques to generate explanations for recommendations.
